Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}圣天空战记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要坠入爱河每个人都会变得如此孤单?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正拥抱着比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切必定都是为了让我俩能绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用泪水来呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早就给了我 最宝贵的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人,您快回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血从操演宫中流出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.32,0:01:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.19,0:01:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听得到我的声音吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,把眼睛张开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快请蜜拉娜公主过来 是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受损的不是只有装甲吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么会伤得那么重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还能战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅…翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙…龙神人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到国王竟然会是龙神人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚特兰提斯之力加上龙神人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么都这个时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身边老是出现些令我不得不想起那个男人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的脉搏极不稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去会有生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是医生吗 快想点办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的能力有限啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说这伤并不普通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是从内侧…肉从体内裂开所形成的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样根本就没办法止血
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯卡弗洛尼的操演宫并没有受损吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟梵一样的伤□
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵感应到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵与艾斯嘉科尼合为一体了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以必须把艾斯嘉科尼修好才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然这样下去,梵会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有阿斯多利亚的商船队出现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快要抵达你的故乡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得说再见了,席尔菲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别露出这种表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美人鱼就该待在海中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容是最美丽的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别再被抓到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还被抓到,你就告诉对方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说你认识阿斯多利亚的德莱甸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷,您竟然花了那么大笔钞票在那尾人鱼上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还要把她放回海里去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会害我挨老爷骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么爱计较嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的东西还是最适合回归自然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是库鲁杰特嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方希望能见您一面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是德莱甸…对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亚第三王女蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是蜜拉娜的未婚夫?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道他是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,就是那个企图绑架你的梅甸之子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他不是很危险吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,若是能够借助他的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定就能找到救梵的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还满意我的书斋吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心跳很剧烈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前我一直以为你只是个任性的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到竟会长成为如此美丽的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真教我感动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也变得高大英挺了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真话吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:07:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就马上回国举行结婚典礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太突然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经是未婚夫妻了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上我又是个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经商成功的超级有钱人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丰富的学识足以媲美学者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然自吹自擂了点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过长相也…帅呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有什么不满的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德…德莱甸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也需要让你做好心理准备喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德莱甸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正欲速则不达
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并不是来找我谈这个的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就进入正题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差解除封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又给我擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的迪兰度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然已经找到能源点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就随我高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是伊斯帕农制的人型装甲?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把它弄得伤痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些武士就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷,小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是德莱甸?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来传说是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么意思,德莱甸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"先生"就免了,叫我德莱甸就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以麻烦你别再卖关子了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古文书上有写
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊斯帕农制的人型装甲会取走驾驶者的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会取走…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶者的性命?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊斯帕农乃继承亚特兰提斯之民智慧的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由他们制作出来的人型装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉由订定血契来决定主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到那个主人死亡为止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时它还会取代其主参与战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当人型装甲受伤倒下时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其主人也会一同倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试着不光只是驾驶艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更在心里进行操演
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再要你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我害他的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把人型装甲修好就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们无法进行如此大规模的修补作业…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊斯帕农制的人型装甲可是有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人叫过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:09:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造出艾斯嘉科尼的伊斯帕农族人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是传说中的伊斯帕农工房船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.69,0:10:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（伊斯帕农语）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（伊斯帕农语）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（伊斯帕农语）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（伊斯帕农语）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔,法尼利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔,法尼利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有问题吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们只是在查看艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五千万
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五…五千万?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼的修理费
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们年薪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2000倍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么贵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果付不出来那我们就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个船队都给你这样如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们花了五年才搜集来的珍品耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您竟然将价值超过八千万的东西给…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德莱甸,我们没办法偿还你那么大笔数目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为王族就别那么小家子气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是很中意那位国王罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你撑着点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿绳子来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用绳子把他绑住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王,你撑着点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绳子拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼的痛楚,他全都感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎扎实实地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德莱甸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要艾斯嘉科尼修理好了,国王的伤就会跟着痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,他得先撑过这些痛苦才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人…梵大人会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他绝对…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会那么简单就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的,他一定可以撑过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是亚特兰提斯之力…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理想未来的鼓动…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痊…痊愈了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没韶下半点伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露,让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到居然真的会治好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是托了大家的福,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,我又被你救了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该向德莱甸与小瞳道谢才对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,这一切都要感谢这位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要小心艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我劝你还是别再驾驶它了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦艾斯嘉科尼受损了,事情又会重演
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一艾斯嘉科尼损毁了,那你也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再让艾斯嘉科尼受损
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好战之人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊斯帕农不想被卷入
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们得离开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是寨巴哈吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,竟然已经追过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血契
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用龙神之血订契
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:16:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊斯帕农无法保障
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法保障?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然逃到那么显眼的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有人型装甲吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别强人所难了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这艘是商船耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装饰用的倒是有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让亚连他们去应付就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠装甲根本就打不赢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就照小瞳说的去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊斯帕农人不也说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说他们无法保障
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可以驾驶艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定能顺利控制艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把舱门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们给我听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天来结束猎龙行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要亲手做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼,给我你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家上！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快用隐形披风
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得到,我看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要为弗雷特王报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要为巴尔卡斯报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究…究竟是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪兰度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪、歇士达、达雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙究竟是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.48,0:20:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对,艾斯嘉科尼不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要为法尼利亚报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.62,0:20:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准你杀害迪兰度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也跟我们一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪兰度大人是我们的恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他将荣耀至极的人型装甲赐给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑选我们进入荣耀至极的龙击队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是…我们绝不让你动他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是…好啦,你就跟我们一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人究竟是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.32,0:22:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是放着不管,梵会…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.15,0:22:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵会被带走的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:57.42,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月儿彼方蓝色探照灯照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:05.87,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降临的天使 你究竟是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:13.50,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的门扉即将开启　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:19.65,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放过这令人兴奋的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.72,0:22:22.01,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:27.02,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃烧般的神秘双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.09,0:22:30.86,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真无邪的笑容让我倾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:34.66,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深处的暗示只传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.73,0:22:38.67,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了无止尽的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:42.17,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心的鼓动无法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.23,0:22:49.64,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想带着你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:57.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:05.86,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:13.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:19.64,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:22.01,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:27.02,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.09,0:22:30.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:34.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.73,0:22:38.66,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:42.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.23,0:22:49.64,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい


